metadata.description:
Cartoons & Cereal an iconic phrase known worldwide and describes a kids favorite Saturday pass-time perfectly! 

Impulse is nothing more than a kid at heart and spares no time once entering RAREwrld and heads off to find the nearest TV set because his favorite show is gearing up to start he gathers his supplies grabs the remote and prepares for Nirvanna.

This is the first installment in an Art Series that will transport you into the world of Blast!
